Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}罪歌：晚上好 巴裘拉：晚上好呀 田中太郎：晚上好~ 賽頓：晚上好~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位有什麼計劃麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠閒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白天談情說愛的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}甘樂進入聊天室
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位好 你們的甘樂來啦~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴裘拉還是這麼過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 各位知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽島幽平的殺人預告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個演員羽島幽平？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為網上的留言引起了軒然大波呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}我要宰了羽島幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}我認識因他變得不幸的女子 我要替天行道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是有人惡作劇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}我是復仇的魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天好不容易休息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下泰平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}天下泰平：即天下太平 指處處平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H542CCB&\an8\fs26}成為恩愛的明星情侶的機會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H7DDE79&\3c&HFFFFFF&}追尋池袋情侶中的No.1!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為恩愛的明星情侶的機會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋池袋情侶中的No.1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是採訪人羽島幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要在我出生的這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池袋尋找最棒的情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被選為No.1的情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以兩人一起在我所出演的電影中出道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界第一的情侶出道企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這企劃居然能通過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幽平事務所的社長說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是戀愛的時代哦Everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將恩愛的情侶一同挖掘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為新偶像推出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把挖掘過程和狀況一起拍攝下來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能變成電視節目了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 幽平 怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要試試當個尋找最佳情侶的愛情丘比特哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要讓我演這種角色的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}恩愛的情侶在哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的來演了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 天氣這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要不要久違的出去散個步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}耽誤您一小會兒可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我想把堆積下來的錄像都看完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞爾堤真是個電視迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽島幽平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒也很喜歡他演的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是靜雄的弟弟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他 是靜雄的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位是在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很般配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男友 女友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？？？？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽島幽平的羽念成wa的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}日語中羽字有はね（hane）和わ（wa）兩種讀法 和也有wa的讀法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就變成和島幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和島幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和島幽 平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和島幽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和島幽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 正確的讀法是平和島幽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}日語中幽可以讀作ゆう（you） 也可以讀作かすか（kasuka）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說過他有個弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你知道折原有妹妹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上中學的雙胞胎妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}現在就去尋找池袋恩愛的情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池袋No.1？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們的愛是世界第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是宇宙第一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼節目？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是最佳情侶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在誠二家裡裝了20個左右的竊聽器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠二很快就利落的全部找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還通過其中的一個對我說早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼宇宙第一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能愛誠二的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 臨也說過今天要去池袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘~終於買了車載電視啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫面很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說No.1情侶的話當然要數龍兒和大河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}neta自龍虎鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻和伊斯卡利伯也很合得來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}neta自撲殺天使 伊斯卡利伯是多庫洛持有武器的名字 櫻童鞋果然是因為相性問題才屢次被撲殺的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽島幽平的話 收到了殺人預告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被修理的估計是襲擊他的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}露西亞壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天初次約會的純真情侶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的初次約會也是在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想著一定要比平時打扮得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是又不願意讓人知道自己用心打扮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生當然不會穿著看膩了的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何比任何時候都讓人心動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約她看電影 她答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 今天不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不管是Dollars的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是正臣的事情都還沒說清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之峰同學約我看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為從那時起就沒提過那天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說什麼 如何表達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話語在腦海中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是什麼都說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到對方的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就什麼都說不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這般美妙的情侶我們能遇見麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 我們就來聽聽這兩位的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您今天是從哪來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}我 我家 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 要是你的影子可以一分為二就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個尋找池袋No.1情侶的企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看不都是在尋找我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 還是應該上街對著攝像機將我們的愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果上了電視 大家肯定會對塞爾堤一見鍾情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淒慘呻吟 東倒西歪  艱難困苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你們兩個在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九琉璃 舞流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 靜雄你知道幽平在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道他今天在池袋錄影 但是居然見不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 介紹幽平給我們認識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們哥哥邊笑邊跑去給卡車撞死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就介紹你們認識
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要臨也哥哥的話送你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…所以說…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 九琉璃姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平 你幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}別打擾幽做節目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她雖然只是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是雖然只是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說也不算是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說我想和她做更進一步的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得現在不是考慮這些的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之峰同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個很重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管對我還是對她來說都很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得再次見到他之前還是不要發生什麼的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算幹嗎啊 「慢半拍」同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想繼續保持現在的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是決定權在她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽島幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別停繼續拍 拍那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有賽門在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們會因為被捲入他們的兄弟愛而掛掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣告牌飛過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個扔過來的是靜雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會有別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 園原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡受傷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}請把我們放下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把門打開啦 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 妹妹們給你添麻煩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你們兄弟感情還是那麼深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傻子是哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會特意告訴我弟弟有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不會認為是因為至今為止我都給小靜添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想以我的方式來贖罪麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是在網上吵著要殺你弟弟的傢伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甩掉他的前任女友是羽島幽平的狂熱粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎一味的認為是因為被幽平搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙碰巧住在池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧看了電視知道在這邊錄影就過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又那麼碰巧帶著刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想都不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直覺真準啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我將幽平的行程告訴他的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想弟弟有危險的話小靜一定會出面的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我決定暫時離開這裡 消失一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走之前要對這裡和我自身做一個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是捉弄你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺言說完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨~也~老~弟~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H55266D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an8\fs28}怪奇！！東京神秘報道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2E2F76&\3c&HFFFFFF&}飛舞的自動販賣機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們攝制組在池袋遇見了相當詭異的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在池袋的一角突然出現的無重力狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架不好哦 肚子會餓的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是大自然對持續破壞生態的人類發出的警告嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去制止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞爾堤 小心鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別上電視了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 有人在濫用科學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要說池袋最速配的一對果然要數小靜和…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來自宇宙的侵略者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降臨地球上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折原臨也？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄正在和人幹架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在嗎 是現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是打倒靜雄的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個黑影是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小靜攻了攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻受交換
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻啊攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受 攻 受 攻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩澤完全被乙女大路的魔力蠱惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞爾堤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要和你來個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我拿下靜雄的人頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無頭騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拍 快拍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0A020A&\3c&H9FBBD4&}和羽島幽平一起去百家池袋名店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大而細緻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥而不膩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}露西亞壽司 好吃！不貴！厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是現場直播…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和島先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然又中了和高中時代一樣的招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點沒長進哎 小靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒長進？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你所謂的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾我們相愛的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰我都不會原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 誠二 我們的愛是最強最無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擋路了 該死的丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 九琉璃姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞爾堤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的奇跡 誠二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊 九琉璃姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}實況轉播靈異事件 黑色的影子的真面目到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(411,372)}出現在池袋的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正在池袋上空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家看看那個黑色的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:20:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}據說在江戶時代在這附近橫行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞爾堤果然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那幫小子都壓制住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本應該感謝你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家不存在這種交易
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就給我老老實實地別動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞爾堤小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}街上聚集的人群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨著各種羈絆和愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會捲入仇恨和惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而為了守護這個城市以及這裡的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池袋署今天也持續戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}保衛城市和平！！零距離！大都會24小時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官大追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然這麼收尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不能上電視了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天有電視直播呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我就在那附近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 碰上了很恐怖的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位也多注意交警啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交警？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來有位超級「慢半拍」男孩上電視了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城市裡嚇人的東西好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣各位還是喜歡池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去來良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是來見學的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡但你還要去死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有我喜歡的人所以很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
